{"tid":1468858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星...咩叫割蓆啊？！","createTime":"2019-08-13T22:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:19:28.000Z","uid":33966,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"385fb6964e45f80d7f7f25e9bbe78bafee9d33a8","tid":1468858,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:14:39.000Z","msg":"咩叫割蓆啊？！割蓆係譴責你從此絕交丫嘛！而家一檢討下有咩做得唔好就俾人話割蓆！我知要尊重前線，冇人唔尊重前線！前線都係人，係人就有機會做得唔夠好，咁大家討論下點樣做好d唔得咩？而家當咗前線係聖人永遠唔會錯啊？咁同另類嘅個人崇拜有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n老老實實共產黨都好過我地，起碼人地識得團結內部識得檢討反省，就算大規模內鬥都係等勝利之後。而且共產黨都識得愈係危急愈係憤怒愈要冷靜，同埋要識得做下表面工夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該你地，唔該大家，思考下不割蓆嘅真正意義！短短幾日已經聞到雨傘後期陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係唔想輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2527bd72781f6826b24de9bd7fd89ea2e2d5fc5e","tid":1468858,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57800cb06234b58867abfe09f21feef97c26ee2","tid":1468858,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:15:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb0552b4ab63947233fb1987213f51207475cc13","tid":1468858,"uid":271051,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:16:22.000Z","msg":"大家有無諗過點解藍絲完全唔會分化？因為佢地會諉過於對家，而我地竟然會諉過於手足。<br />\n<br />\n例子，我藍絲親戚死都唔信黑警室內放催淚彈，有晒片都話係黃媒抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n請大家向藍絲學習。"},{"pid":"07c6546bd1e954c431d437818a013e970e9b3ae8","tid":1468858,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-